          <td valign="top"><p class="nameRub"><strong>
	Welcome to Sochi 



</strong></p><p class=textOsn>Riviera Sochi travel company founded jn 1999 provides a wide set of travel services to tourist in popular resort destinations of South Russia: Greater Sochi, Krasnaya Polyana, Anapa, Gelendzhik, Tuapse, Goryachiy Kluch, Yeysk etc. We offer an array of various services for individuals and tourist groups, and also for business travel. We ensure immidiate response, reasonable prices and high end customer-oriented solutions. Our experience, in-depth knowledge of destinations allow us to offer exclusive tourist programmes, high class services, theme parties, the best choice of hotels and restaurants, memorable excursions, teambuilding and outdoor activities, familization with the hospitable cultures of Kuban province and the Cuacusus.</P><p class=textOsn>Our&nbsp;prices for accomodation are in Russian Roubles.&nbsp;The Invoice for accommodation will be billed in Roubles or Euro as per the received application form in conformity with the Central Bank抯 rate of exchange on the date the Invoice is issued including 2% conversion fee. You can pay our invoice by bank transfer or credit card. If you prefer to pay by credit card&nbsp;the Invoice will be billed in Roubles including 3% commission.<BR></P><p class=textOsn></P><p class=textOsn><STRONG>There are so many reasons to come to Sochi:</STRONG><STRONG><BR></STRONG>^ It is worth visiting the famous&nbsp; resort&nbsp; that have got the name of&nbsp; Black Sea Riviera and the south capital of Russia.<BR>^ Did you see magnolia, yucca and oleander in fool bloom? Nobody will be indifferent to the unique nature of Sochi!<BR>^ It抯 splendid to have a picnic in canyon near mountain stream, to enjoy forest抯 fragrance, stillness and the cleanest fresh air!<BR>^ Within an hour you can get from seacoast to mountain tops, to Alpine meadows.<BR>^ Children like dolphins, monkeys, ostriches, peacocks, bear cubs, deers and raccoons.<BR>^ There are entertainments for any taste: aqua-parks, recreation parks, side shows, casinos, discos, nightclubs, fireworks, showprogrammes&nbsp;and star concerts, theatre &amp; cinema premieres in the open air halls, festivals&nbsp;and exhibitions.<BR>^ The gourmets don抰 remain unmoved by particular dishes offered by a large number of urban and country restaurants and taverns.</P>


